Insect Families of the US & Canada

This is a list of all the insect families found in the United States and Canada, organized by order, and curated by GM. If you find any errors, please contact GM at montgomery.graham AT gmail.com. Taxonomic authorities used as references for this list can be found at the bottom of the page.
